  "rules": [
    "This proposal is non-executable: no config.json, runner authorization, GPU lease, or seed consumption may exist before Fable acceptance and a separate immutable launch authorization.",
    "Every generation, evaluation attempt, and analyzer launch requires an Ed25519-signed one-shot token, an external consumed marker, a signed execution receipt, and bubblewrap isolation with no network or credential mounts.",
    "All three arms within a replicate use identical training and per-generation evaluation seeds; only the reach30 residual dose differs.",
    "The common 4096-game block is public development evidence and can select at most one arm; it cannot confirm or promote that arm.",
    "Every endpoint must be rerun once with the identical checkpoint and seed block; exact per-game telemetry and replay-trace hashes must match before the outcome-blind input authorization can open analysis.",
    "A later fresh public confirmation, private/status-3, multiplayer, exploitability, fairness, latency, regression, and Michael gate remain mandatory.",
    "No outcome-conditioned retry, seed substitution, arm substitution, or early promotion is permitted.",
    "A consumed authorization may recover only through the frozen guardian-classified recovery policy. Any unclassified, ambiguous, outcome-dependent, or second failure permanently closes this campaign instance."
  ]
